&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Image&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://images.openai.com/static-rsc-4/hoA1j88c3KEhEX9quQQVWJuYx70Qwyzp--NJIz5lQab68XaIn8DcAHvw6CWQYrh7k_pANdyjCeqxeJgByYSxTndNY4m6QAZp7wRUE1CXfMg0Ulw_I5Ar3gksLQ4hQi1ETHLXMxVHvbeZ8dQ8lXyAudsgUFZ6qnaHLsnqmSHCb2uwE0AV9RTYEbENjWlSqhfI?purpose=fullsize&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Image&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://images.openai.com/static-rsc-4/GCzcoC0ID9ipUMYyqaSrkD7lP6oV3WufXIAO9mehP9guEDr26vkdW_sC7I0y09UJQ7xJEQCyOHHKL6d0YvM0eaJofmM_dvL52ceihyMeyJuAIDEMX4kNureP1sM9VqVjqRFsmA6q6v4s-7to_JdsImoqphaVidRsvhLbDnp2iVfnIOnkpiCtanUYV6swHl89?purpose=fullsize&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Image&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://images.openai.com/static-rsc-4/IPEPju1znaZrRjY94r6fOlWhSWpTOKBo7ssjaiiJy1Igafb9dYh1i22C3XQXQ8Cg0DB3uKeBOVywAVJY3AKuyJsXyCGXmraFqEjlixDU9SetT7BA4F9CrwVE509MoewNPS0ZvPjidt6UNyybf5SJ5wN2k8lmBoe00h9gGkCDMoBzRsqIUugJnWlBw4-ToKPo?purpose=fullsize&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;性格特点&#34;&gt;性格特点&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;稳健型&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;工程管理派&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;长期主义&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;国家战略执行者&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;风险控制强&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;对公司影响力&#34;&gt;对公司影响力&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;高，但同时受沙特国家能源政策深度影响。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
